[I] A graphical browser for the Gemini protocol

[T] Lagrange is a graphical browser for the gemini protocol using SDL2.
[T] It as tabs, bookmarks, TLS like regular web browsers.
[T] It also supports downloading and playing audio and image files directly
[T] from it.

[U] https://git.skyjake.fi/skyjake/lagrange

